## Monthly Batch Workflow

For recurring monthly extraction of the latest episode from each tracked series.

### Series List

Tracked series are listed in `app/handlers/NOTES.md` under the **"Monthly Series"** section. Each entry has:
- Series URL (e.g. `https://takecomic.jp/series/8e32550d65684`)
- Reader name (e.g. `takecomic`)
- Short name for output folder (e.g. `yume-furarete-yuri`)

### Workflow Steps

1. **For each series**: visit the series URL, find the latest free episode link (`/episodes/{hash}`)
2. **Extract**: run `bun cli/extract.ts --reader {reader} --url {episode_url} --out ./output/{short_name}`
3. **Verify**: run `bun cli/verify.ts --input ./output/{short_name}`
4. **Sanity check**: visually confirm extracted pages
5. **Update NOTES.md**: record which episode was grabbed and the date

### Output Structure

```
output/
  {short_name}/                          # One folder per series
    {Title} Ch-{NN}.zip                  # ZIP from handler (auto-named by page title)
    {Title} Ch-{NN}_extracted/           # From verify.ts --input {zip}
      {Title} Ch-{NN}/
        Ch-{NN} Pg-001.png
        Ch-{NN} Pg-002.png
        ...
      viewer.html
```

Example after grabbing latest from two series:

```
output/
  yume-furarete-yuri/
    夢でフラれてはじまる百合・51話 _ 竹コミ！.zip
    夢でフラれてはじまる百合・51話 _ 竹コミ！_extracted/
      夢でフラれてはじまる百合・51話 _ 竹コミ！/
        Ch-51 Pg-001.png
        Ch-51 Pg-002.png
        ...
      viewer.html
  another-manga/
    ...
```

### Finding the Latest Episode

For takecomic series pages, episodes are listed newest-first. The first link with "無料" (free) badge is the latest free episode. Paid episodes show a coin cost (e.g. "90"). To access paid episodes, use `--profile` with a logged-in Chrome profile.

To find the latest episode URL from a series page:
1. Fetch the series page HTML
2. Parse episode links -- they follow the pattern `/episodes/{hash}`
3. The first link in the list is the newest episode
